DAY-9

Aaj ka kaam (ScoreCard System & Performance Metrics)

1) ScoreCard Controller & Service
- ScoreCardController banaya with comprehensive analytics:
  - POST /api/scorecards → create new scorecard
  - GET /api/users/{userId}/scorecard → get user's scorecard
  - PUT /api/scorecards/{id} → update scorecard metrics
  - POST /api/users/{userId}/scorecard/generate → auto-generate scorecard

2) Performance Metrics Calculation
- ScoreCardService me advanced analytics:
  - Accuracy calculation based on quiz performance
  - Consistency tracking across learning sessions
  - Discipline score based on regular learning habits
  - Dedication metrics from time spent learning
  - Streak calculation for motivation

3) Auto ScoreCard Generation
- generateOrUpdateScoreCard() method:
  - User ke quiz results se accuracy calculate karta hai
  - Progress data se consistency metrics nikalta hai
  - Daily learning patterns se discipline score banata hai
  - Total learning time se dedication calculate karta hai

4) Performance Summary API
- GET /api/users/{userId}/performance-summary endpoint:
  - Human-readable performance summary
  - Improvement suggestions
  - Streak achievements aur motivational messages

5) ScoreCard Analytics Dashboard Data
- Comprehensive metrics for frontend dashboard:
  - Learning velocity trends
  - Topic-wise performance breakdown
  - Weekly/monthly progress graphs data
  - Comparative analysis with peer learners

Testing Done
- ScoreCard generation working with real user data.
- Performance metrics accurately calculated.
- Summary reports generating properly.

Next Steps (DAY-10)
- Learning Path system implement karna hai.
- Structured learning journeys create karna hai.
- Path recommendation engine add karna hai.

